data.description: Home built in 2018. There are 19 solar panels on the roof (Energy efficient). Comfortable and cozy that is close to shopping, dining, and numerous entertainment activities. All furniture is available for purchase over the home price.
data.whatILove: Close to the Pinnacle and Downtown Bristol. Walmart, Sams, and Target all within a very few miles. Schools are nearby as well. Great neighborhood and neighbors. Two accesses to I-81 (Exit 5 and Exit 7). Growing community. Call for an appointment to view house or see Open House dates and times. We love this home and the area, but we are relocating back to East Tennessee. Shopping, bowling, movie theaters, many dining options, and downtown Bristol is all within 7 miles of the home.
